snippet.title: 10 Cities 10 Reporters: Impact of Demonetisation on Businesses and Markets

localized.description:
Watch India TV's exclusive report '10 cities, 10 reporters' to know the impact of demonetisation on your businesses and markets. Modi government has banned currency notes of Rs 500 adn Rs 1000 to curb black money,  fake currency, terrorism. More than fifty per cent industries are closed in many cities.
